<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.9">
<l>tikkuniṟai pukaḻāḷaṉ tīvēḷvic ceṉṟanāḷ</l>
<l>mikkaperuñ capainaṭuvē villiṟuttāṉ mōtiramkaṇ</l>
<l>ṭokkumā laṭaiyāḷa maṉumāṉeṉ ṟuccimēl</l>
<l>vaittukkoṇ ṭukantaṉaḷāl malarkkuḻalāḷ cītaiyumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The day when [he] went to the fire sacrifice of the ruler</l>
<l rend="indent">whose praise pervades the eight quarters,</l>
<l>in the middle of the very big assembly, he broke the bow.</l>
<l>Seeing the ring, Sītā, with blossom [filled] tresses,</l>
<l rend="indent">holding [it] high, rejoiced, saying,</l>
<l>“This proof is indeed acceptable, Hanuman!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
